**Story**
Once upon a time, in a forest, there lived a monkey recided on a banana tree, which was on the bank of a river and in the same forest there lived a crocodile and his wife
one day crocodile came to the bank of the river and rested under the tree. The kind hearted monnkey offered him somne fruits. The Crocodile came backthe day for more fruits, as he loved those fruits. As the day passed by , the crocodile and the monkey became the best friends.
